{"tid":2333321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"湯告魯斯疑搭上美國隊長老婆","createTime":"2020-12-20T09:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T13:28:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e00882a7f1058cac0c0ce446f9124b50cb9a6bb","tid":2333321,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"荷里活巨星湯告魯斯（Tom Cruise）近日忙於為新片《職業特工隊7》（Mission Impossible 7）開工，日前他在片場鬧爆工作人員沒有嚴格執行防疫措施，最後5名劇組人員離職，事件成為近期網民熱話。<br />\n<br />\n一波未平一波又起，消息指湯告魯斯跟同片拍檔、在Marvel電影世界飾演美國隊長另一半Peggy Carter的38歲女星Hayley Atwell秘密撻著，仲話二人好快會公開戀情！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201220/417353453061279744042756.jpeg/vNb4KZURzJ15a-QMkw9O8pxnQQEQVMRfgfG19oHxtfY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201220%2F417353453061279744042756.jpeg%2FvNb4KZURzJ15a-QMkw9O8pxnQQEQVMRfgfG19oHxtfY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0fd5cec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHayley Atwell在IG分享跟湯告魯斯的合照。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n現年58歲的湯告魯斯雖然比Hayley Atwell年長廿載，但保養得宜的他看起來年年輕得多，跟女方在一起相當合襯。Hayley Atwell參演第7及第8集《職業特工隊》，跟湯告魯斯有大量對手戲，二人在片場亦不時「放閃」，言談甚歡之外，未埋位都會拖到實，難怪會傳緋聞。據現場工作人員透露，湯告魯斯跟Hayley Atwell於開工第一日便撻著，後來因為新冠肺炎疫情令拍攝中斷，二人就有更多時間相處，感情迅速升溫，後來女方更到男方的倫敦寓所見面，似乎打得火熱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201220/417353697366904832912436.jpeg/FKdpq0vR9h8a5fTanZYTpy3voZFIOz8XezpuKHs6big?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201220%2F417353697366904832912436.jpeg%2FFKdpq0vR9h8a5fTanZYTpy3voZFIOz8XezpuKHs6big%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b434099a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHayley Atwell飾演的Peggy Carter在《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》跟美國隊長有美滿結局。（劇照）<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01. com/電影/564072</code></pre>"},{"pid":"720ff202730f33840f8ade9ab47ad32c93d984b5","tid":2333321,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c136d3247e5b0de8b3dcea437e297c0e3128e6e1","tid":2333321,"uid":6826,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"條女好撚大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1d02d35978618499ad0f73199a420c4a9c0b50","tid":2333321,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"日日夾美國巨腸"},{"pid":"62434f18bd78c994f89a1ad097c4583d46dde57d","tid":2333321,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c136d3247e5b0de8b3dcea437e297c0e3128e6e1","tid":2333321,"uid":6826,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:04:13.000Z","msg":"條女好撚大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"526dfb63c98b017936ae7cc8b7bda1ea2bdf6888","tid":2333321,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b737457d3937fd91526bb057400fbcdeeb40372f","tid":2333321,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"美國隊長肯定揪贏白面仔"},{"pid":"e232e45ca767ad49db10a632a488284e39206dd5","tid":2333321,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b737457d3937fd91526bb057400fbcdeeb40372f","tid":2333321,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"美國隊長肯定揪贏白面仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"身高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bd0b996136f1a40c36d7052488e491a01b04de","tid":2333321,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"巨腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f3868ac2576678f76f71c6e